column5: Me too bro. Im 15 and ive been struggling and wanting to end life for ages. I've promised people that I wouldn't end my life but its doesn't matter anymore. Nothing does. Im dumb and have no future in life. Im sorry if i didnt comfort you or anything but im just here to tell you im also someone that relates to your post
I feel like ppl who are depressed relate to other depressed ppl so they help others. Idk about you guys but that basiacally sums it up for me
